Twisty Passages - A simple rogue-like dungeon crawler
Copyright (C) 2020  Elliot Dronebarger

This program is currently designed to work only with the ncurses library.
To compile, you will need:
- The ncurses library and headers (ncurses-dev)
- The yaml-cpp submodule

Building:
git submodule update --init
mkdir ext/yaml-cpp/build
cd ext/yaml-cpp/build && cmake -DYAML_BUILD_SHARED_LIBS=ON ..
make

cd ../../..
mkdir build && cd build
cmake ..
make

This program is IN DEVELOPMENT. It is missing a lot of features
---------------------------------------------------------------
There are no monsters or items yet.
